                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2002-01-09</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>The Diamond Sutra features text and commentaries translated from the Chinese and Sanskrit by Red Pine, providing all interested in Buddhist teachings with new insights on the most studied of all the sutras. The author is a Buddhist scholar who has consulted dozens of commentaries in the course of his research, making for an exceptional translation.</span>
                  
              
